| Model              | Description                        |
| ------------------ | ---------------------------------- |
| CNN                | Basic convolutional neural network |
| CNN + Augmentation | Improved CNN using augmentation    |

| Model              | Accuracy   |
| ------------------ | ---------- |
| Basic CNN          | ~75%       |
| CNN + Augmentation | ~85%       |

Data Augmentation Techniques

Image rotation

Zooming

Horizontal flipping

Rescaling

Purpose:
To reduce overfitting and improve model generalization.


| Challenge             | Solution                    |
| --------------------- | --------------------------- |
| Small dataset         | Data augmentation           |
| Overfitting           | Dropout + transfer learning |
| Different image sizes | Image resizing              |



